  "3166200": {
    "name": "Across the Abyss: Voidborn",
    "steam_appid": 3166200,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/6e3474cc7b9d4e8e4d9e212d581d48e0.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/1ba9c54bb574576074a9f38afab2fb85.poster.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/1ba9c54bb574576074a9f38afab2fb85.webm?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/1ba9c54bb574576074a9f38afab2fb85.mp4?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款2D像素风格的Roguelike游戏中，敌人不仅仅是障碍——他们是你的武器！把爆炸性的敌人扔进战场，引发混乱的连锁反应，一次消灭多个敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/149b6d40582292284316c3e03c08c24e.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/d4dbcd3ebd123f8d279e2f50a4b3d58b.poster.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/d4dbcd3ebd123f8d279e2f50a4b3d58b.webm?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/d4dbcd3ebd123f8d279e2f50a4b3d58b.mp4?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >越走得远，你就变得越强大！收集强化道具和升级，增强角色的能力，让你有更好的机会进入更混乱的层级。你能挑战到什么高度？<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/72b121135f174f38a7c5230484fdb076.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/6f6b5c73b6a52bbb84a2f85622e0b1ee.poster.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/6f6b5c73b6a52bbb84a2f85622e0b1ee.webm?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/6f6b5c73b6a52bbb84a2f85622e0b1ee.mp4?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >测试你的技能，挑战一系列搞笑的BOSS。每个BOSS提供独特的挑战，旨在考验你的能力，同时保持轻松有趣的游戏体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/b44e3aa7fc76e53195ed98f840e750cc.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=86 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/626f7f78c959d5c2de9c5ae61b26ee6c.poster.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/626f7f78c959d5c2de9c5ae61b26ee6c.webm?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/626f7f78c959d5c2de9c5ae61b26ee6c.mp4?t=1754946342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇见一群性格各异的古怪角色。他们可能会帮助你，也可能成为你的障碍，但无论如何，这些角色为你的冒险之旅增添了幽默感和不可预测性。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166200/extras/4a7940942102458ee74eab62e550a421.avif?t=1754946342\" width=600 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏以搞笑的方式重新诠释传统的动作游戏，不会太过严肃。准备好在这个充满爆炸和不可预测的世界中笑个不停吧！</p>",
